Time":"2017-11-14T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"就在附加賽進行前，伊巴被問到有關他的國家隊會否能夠晉身世界盃決賽週。伊巴表示：「我退出國家隊後，瑞典國家隊便沒有了壓力，因為外界不再對他們有太多的期待。當我還踢的時候，水平明顯提高了，如今沒有了我，球隊水平便下降了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fhotblood%2F%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%2599%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%259F%259F-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BA%2586-c1301085.html&d=UPjA6PuRRITyKL%2B8B9ZvRCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=dff8a13c\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f51f8fd177f2227ebf9b7d19d321d7828b578c4","tid":468153,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就在附加賽進行前，伊巴被問到有關他的國家隊會否能夠晉身世界盃決賽週。伊巴表示：「我退出國家隊後，瑞典國家隊便沒有了壓力，因為外界不再對他們有太多的期待。當我還踢的時候，水平明顯提高了，如今沒有了我，球隊水平便下降了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fhotblood%2F%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%2599%25E8%258E%25AB%25E5%259F%259F-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2585%25B8-%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BA%2586-c1301085.html&d=UPjA6PuRRITyKL%2B8B9ZvRCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=dff8a13c\" target=\"_blank\">http://football.fanpiece.com/hotblood/%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3-%E4%BC%8A%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%99%E8%8E%AB%E5%9F%9F-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8-%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D%E4%BA%86-c1301085.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燈"},{"pid":"2fa33e39cc454db19062590faeb9947e21547a51","tid":468153,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"佢唔出返黎踢我切<br />\n到時又乜柒I am back"},{"pid":"29e941d37b228b2d905ccecf458398924656ceb0","tid":468153,"uid":26862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I am not thinking about Sweden or the World Cup,&rdquo; he told Sky Sports Italy. &ldquo;I am just thinking about returning to full fitness as soon as possible. My story with the national team is finished. Maybe I could have done more, maybe I could have done less but my time [with them] has come to an end. Either way it would be beautiful if Sweden reached the World Cup.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Now, when I am not a part of the team they are playing with less pressure. People are expecting less. When I was there everyone expected that the team would win the World Cup or the Euros. My impression is that that has changed now and that they will play without any pressure whatsoever and have nothing to lose.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If I listened to my ego then Sweden would, of course, be a better team with me,&rdquo; added Ibrahimovic. &ldquo;But the team has done it really well so far, secured second place in a difficult group [ahead of Holland] and been given this chance to play in the play-offs. The strength of this team is the group.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"6e11459dd87d2eacc4df36eef2587e0ace792c72","tid":468153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢唔出返黎踢我切<br />\n到時又乜柒I am back</blockquote><br />\n開記招順便宣傳個人品牌"},{"pid":"6d1f336aa17781ee3f1c354823b0aad8c4b760b1","tid":468153,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢唔出返黎踢我切<br />\n到時又乜柒I am back</blockquote><br />\n開記招順便宣傳個人品牌</blockquote><br />\n講真佢就算彈出彈入都係比我地j霸氣"},{"pid":"d526a9117fb5fb4afff8e1c1daf8bb7e4f82ffcc","tid":468153,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔出返黎踢我切<br />\n到時又乜柒I am back</blockquote><br />\n開記招順便宣傳個人品牌</blockquote><br />\n講真佢就算彈出彈入都係比我地j霸氣</blockquote><br />\n霸氣回歸"},{"pid":"54ea5aefdde2f53c892c979caccec2354016f58d","tid":468153,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢唔出返黎踢我切<br />\n到時又乜柒I am back</blockquote><br />\n開記招順便宣傳個人品牌</blockquote><br />\n講真佢就算彈出彈入都係比我地j霸氣</blockquote><br />\n霸氣回歸</blockquote><br />\n伊巴彈出彈入=霸氣<br />\n小花彈出彈入=小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d624042306c958dca73bcee4a87a2d4758adb6","tid":468153,"uid":41660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"復出助教拎光環"},{"pid":"8c98a579e7403a4971f5c578b7b13094e262517a","tid":468153,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我黎啦"},{"pid":"77b62970b841346115dcff8983344223309e5bef","tid":468153,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>復出助教拎光環</blockquote><br />\n做啦啦隊算啦<br />\n對腳咁長踢下腿應該幾好睇"},{"pid":"e4d6ead5b0b243cf031186b61b8f0db331391986","tid":468153,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&ldquo;I am not thinking about Sweden or the World Cup,&rdquo; he told Sky Sports Italy. &ldquo;I am just thinking about returning to full fitness as soon as possible. My story with the national team is finished. Maybe I could have done more, maybe I could have done less but my time [with them] has come to an end. Either way it would be beautiful if Sweden reached the World Cup.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Now, when I am not a part of the team they are playing with less pressure. People are expecting less. When I was there everyone expected that the team would win the World Cup or the Euros. My impression is that that has changed now and that they will play without any pressure whatsoever and have nothing to lose.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If I listened to my ego then Sweden would, of course, be a better team with me,&rdquo; added Ibrahimovic. &ldquo;But the team has done it really well so far, secured second place in a difficult group [ahead of Holland] and been given this chance to play in the play-offs. The strength of this team is the group.&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n上面篇翻譯差到呢"}]}